title: Call-Up
description: Jakey a teddy boy, initially acts tough, Ken all bright eyed, Matthew out of his depth, Bruce angry at his situation. Marsh happy to make their lives hell, tries to break their spirits, they have to find ways to survive the demoralization.

title: 36-Hour Pass
description: First leave, Marsh tries to mess it up. Leckie misses train so can't leave. We met Agnes, Matthew's sister, she gives the others a lift, Ken is enamored. Rival Teddy boys mess with car so they are back late, this give Marsh great joy.
